      <title>土耳其建筑股因叙利亚重建押注而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/turkish-building-stocks-surge-on-syria-reconstruction-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以水泥和钢铁制造商为首的土耳其建筑相关类股飙升，因为投资者押注这些公司将在巴沙尔·阿萨德政权迅速垮台后在邻国叙利亚的重建中发挥关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/turkish-building-stocks-surge-on-syria-reconstruction-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:17:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士信贷即将接受调查，瑞银资本受牵连</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/swiss-probe-of-credit-suisse-nears-with-ubs-capital-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士即将公布一项具有里程碑意义的政治调查，调查对象为瑞信 2023 年破产的原因，该报告可能会追究危机责任，并为瑞银集团未来的监管定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/swiss-probe-of-credit-suisse-nears-with-ubs-capital-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:09:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国可能在演习中限制领空 台湾保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/taiwan-on-alert-as-china-restricts-airspace-in-potential-drills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾称，中国限制了其东南沿海的空域，并派遣海军舰艇靠近海峡，这表明北京可能在世界上最紧张的地缘政治热点地区之一举行军事演习。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/taiwan-on-alert-as-china-restricts-airspace-in-potential-drills</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国放松货币政策立场，承诺提供更多财政支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普下个月上任，北京方面准备应对第二场贸易战，中国高层领导计划明年放松货币政策并扩大财政支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-shifts-monetary-policy-stance-for-first-time-since-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称当选后首次与习近平沟通</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/trump-says-for-first-time-he-communicated-with-xi-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他最近几天与中国国家主席习近平进行了交流，这是自这位美国前总统去年 11 月连任以来，两人首次明显保持直接接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/trump-says-for-first-time-he-communicated-with-xi-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《鱿鱼游戏》制片人加入电影界呼吁罢免韩国领导人的行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/-squid-game-maker-joins-film-industry-call-to-oust-korea-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《乌贼游戏》的作者黄东赫与数百名韩国演员和导演一道呼吁弹劾或罢免总统尹锡烈，让韩国最强大的行业之一与这位陷入困境的领导人对抗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/-squid-game-maker-joins-film-industry-call-to-oust-korea-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 07:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叛国罪调查后韩国总统面临何种未来？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-can-president-yoon-be-arrested-investigated-for-treason</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在弹劾投票中幸存下来，但继续执政并不能使他在实施戒严的灾难性尝试后免受调查。检察官和警方已对他的叛国罪指控展开调查。法律程序可能会拖延数月甚至数年，如果被判有罪，他可能会面临终身监禁或——尽管可能性不大——死刑。虽然韩国已经判处前总统叛国罪，并弹劾了另外两名总统]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korea-can-president-yoon-be-arrested-investigated-for-treason</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 05:40:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国调查升级 尹永康被禁止出国旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korean-police-consider-overseas-travel-ban-on-yoon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国禁止总统尹锡烈出国旅行，一系列调查使这位陷入困境的领导人因其混乱的戒严令宣布而面临被拘留的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/south-korean-police-consider-overseas-travel-ban-on-yoon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 04:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农业信贷银行在意大利建立防御体系以对抗意大利联合信贷银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/credit-agricole-moves-to-shield-italian-business-against-unicredit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）对其规模较小的意大利竞争对手发出收购要约后，法国农业信贷银行（Credit Agricole SA）增持 Banco BPM 股份的举措旨在保护其在意大利的商业利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/credit-agricole-moves-to-shield-italian-business-against-unicredit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 10:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳前总统有望在选举中击败执政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/ghana-election-john-mahama-s-opposition-set-to-win-as-npp-s-bawumia-concedes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳反对党领袖约翰·马哈马有望在 12 月 7 日的总统选举中以 30 多年来的最大优势获胜，此前选民批评执政党未能解决这个世界第二大可可生产国的失控通货膨胀问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/ghana-election-john-mahama-s-opposition-set-to-win-as-npp-s-bawumia-concedes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 09:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
